### Query A — Find Individual Herds with AMS Findings AND Pre-Submit Status AND Active Registration

**Sources:** Query 70 + Query 87 + Query 93 from reference document
**Used for:** TC-AMS-01 primary test data

**Audit note:**
Query 70 alone (`VWBS_AMS_NOTIFIED_HERD`) is insufficient — it returns AMS notified herds
regardless of application status. A Submitted herd (app_mde_code=4) would also appear,
violating the Pre-Submit precondition. Query 87 provides the correct pre-submit filter using
`app_mde_code IN (1,2,3)` — Not Started(1), Renewal Paper(2), Draft(3). Query 93 adds
`bcus_bus_end_date > SYSDATE` from `vwco_biss_business_details` to exclude expired herd
registrations. All three combined give the correct, complete test data set.

```sql
-- Query 70 (AMS notified) + Query 87 (pre-submit) + Query 93 (active registration)
-- Returns individual herds that:
--   1. Have AMS Red findings (VWBS_AMS_NOTIFIED_HERD — Q70)
--   2. Are Pre-Submit — Not Started(1), Renewal Paper(2) or Draft(3) (Q87)
--   3. Have an active herd registration bcus_bus_end_date > SYSDATE (Q93)
SELECT ams.herd_no,
       ams.scheme_year,
       ams.expired,
       a.app_mde_code,
       a.mde_desc        AS app_status,
       bbd.bcus_bus_end_date
FROM VWBS_AMS_NOTIFIED_HERD ams
JOIN vwbs_application a
    ON  a.app_herd_no  = ams.herd_no
    AND a.app_year     = ams.scheme_year
    AND a.app_mde_code IN (1, 2, 3)      -- Pre-Submit: Not Started / Renewal Paper / Draft
JOIN vwco_biss_business_details bbd
    ON  bbd.bcus_bus_id    = ams.herd_no
    AND bbd.bcus_role_code = 100
    AND bbd.bcus_bus_end_date > SYSDATE  -- Active herd registration only
WHERE ams.scheme_year = 2026
AND   ams.expired     = 0
AND   ROWNUM <= 10
ORDER BY ams.herd_no;
```

