### Query E — Find Herds with NO AMS Findings (Negative Test)

**Source:** Query 70 negated + Query 87 (pre-submit) + Query 93 (active)
**Used for:** TC-AMS-02 — confirms panel is absent for herds with no findings

**Audit note:**
`NOT EXISTS` against `VWBS_AMS_NOTIFIED_HERD` ensures the herd has no AMS notification.
Query 87 filter (`app_mde_code IN (1,2,3)`) ensures pre-submit status.
Query 93 filter (`bcus_bus_end_date > SYSDATE`) ensures active registration.

```sql
-- Pre-submit, active herds with NO AMS notifications
-- Combines Q87 (pre-submit) + Q93 (active) + NOT EXISTS Q70 (no AMS)
SELECT a.app_herd_no,
       a.app_mde_code,
       a.mde_desc
FROM vwbs_application a
JOIN vwco_biss_business_details bbd
    ON  bbd.bcus_bus_id    = a.app_herd_no
    AND bbd.bcus_role_code = 100
    AND bbd.bcus_bus_end_date > SYSDATE
WHERE a.app_year     = 2026
AND   a.app_mde_code IN (1, 2, 3)
AND   NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM VWBS_AMS_NOTIFIED_HERD ams
    WHERE ams.herd_no     = a.app_herd_no
    AND   ams.scheme_year = a.app_year
)
AND ROWNUM <= 10
ORDER BY a.app_herd_no;
```

